WEBVTT

b3c3681f-94a0-4353-8581-0ea871041056-0
00:00:01.080 --> 00:00:04.036
Digital calendar applications
are a great way to keep track of

b3c3681f-94a0-4353-8581-0ea871041056-1
00:00:04.036 --> 00:00:06.805
meetings and tasks on your own
or with the people you work

b3c3681f-94a0-4353-8581-0ea871041056-2
00:00:06.805 --> 00:00:07.040
with.

8b65e0e2-25e2-4d91-9a17-d10cdc8c7f75-0
00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:10.952
Unlike traditional paper
calendars or date books, digital

8b65e0e2-25e2-4d91-9a17-d10cdc8c7f75-1
00:00:10.952 --> 00:00:14.016
calendar software makes it easy
to keep your schedule synced

8b65e0e2-25e2-4d91-9a17-d10cdc8c7f75-2
00:00:14.016 --> 00:00:14.920
with other people.

7f9e46e4-906f-48f9-b737-c47f66f0c969-0
00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:18.244
So if you schedule, reschedule,
or cancel meetings or

7f9e46e4-906f-48f9-b737-c47f66f0c969-1
00:00:18.244 --> 00:00:21.401
appointments, everyone's
calendar is updated to reflect

7f9e46e4-906f-48f9-b737-c47f66f0c969-2
00:00:21.401 --> 00:00:22.360
that information.

4d35b805-7ba6-42a6-a795-8b2ae441aa4f-0
00:00:23.280 --> 00:00:26.254
There are lots of popular
calendar apps used across

4d35b805-7ba6-42a6-a795-8b2ae441aa4f-1
00:00:26.254 --> 00:00:29.801
multiple platforms, including
Google Calendar, Apple Calendar

4d35b805-7ba6-42a6-a795-8b2ae441aa4f-2
00:00:29.801 --> 00:00:31.060
and Microsoft Outlook.

845f0572-677c-41af-bb83-d36c00ae8e27-0
00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:34.732
In this chapter, we'll be
focusing on Outlook because in

845f0572-677c-41af-bb83-d36c00ae8e27-1
00:00:34.732 --> 00:00:37.125
addition to it being a
professional calendar

845f0572-677c-41af-bb83-d36c00ae8e27-2
00:00:37.125 --> 00:00:40.157
application, it's also a
full-fledged e-mail application

845f0572-677c-41af-bb83-d36c00ae8e27-3
00:00:40.157 --> 00:00:43.455
and Contact Manager, so you can
easily keep your appointments

845f0572-677c-41af-bb83-d36c00ae8e27-4
00:00:43.455 --> 00:00:46.540
and other tasks synced between
yourself and others in one

845f0572-677c-41af-bb83-d36c00ae8e27-5
00:00:46.540 --> 00:00:46.860
place.